Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这份真情实感　好想将它传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不沉溺于一去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧拥抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷于那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方应该有什么正等待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着那未完结的故事　飞奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀着一颗真诚的心向着那千难万险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开心灵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循环传递着一个讯息　幸福就存于这胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来的少许勇气　尽管须以眼泪相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但这或许正是变强的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖的迭句　想要永远将这份珍重守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心绪交织　感受着这其中的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以说没有人是孤身只影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片蓝天下　好想将这份真情实感传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吃火锅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知怎么回事  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天肉卖的特别便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个白痴一样更兴奋一点儿如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就先开吃啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊你  这么突然！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！别专挑肉吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本来就是我的肉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  肉还好多呢  别吵架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:19.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第9碗  难以掩饰了吧？阿珍的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然觉得自己好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能好好听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有超能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天是炸虾  今天是火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭吃什么我全都梦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是预知梦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…但你堂堂正正地说些过去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再说这是预知谁信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我说对了明天晚饭吃什么  你会相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  你说对了我就信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就今晚  等我梦见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的身体温暖起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也进来泡吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在比较忙  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事请在提示音后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在旁边哦  在便利店旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  这都怪你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那红色的棒子…是什么玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡萝卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿珍会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  阿真那家伙心里到底怎么想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直说讨厌穿女装  但看似乐在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天问问他本人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  那什么预知梦怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我总算是记得点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是说不出来啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！我就知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预知梦个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我等一下  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有重要的事跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说  内田很讨厌吃年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？突然说什么啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田还是吃年糕的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们假设内田讨厌吃年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让内田不断吃她讨厌的年糕的过程中渐渐喜欢上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  会更讨厌年糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  看你用什么方法让她吃了  也不是没可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到身边的人影响  人也会改变嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能变好也能变坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己会做什么预知梦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是身边的人一直无视她  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间久了也就不会再提了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟那是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～预知梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  突然就这么说  吓我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得今天少了点儿东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天保坂学长请假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  请问有事吗  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到升学指导室来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  我想跟你谈的其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道交换留学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望成绩优秀的你能作为我们学校的代表过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？但是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能有很多不便  但这是个机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着年轻好好见识一下这广阔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接触各种各样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会对你有所帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无视眼前正在犯愁的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你有烦恼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才能准确地记住自己做过的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说点儿好办法来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醒就记下来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能行！这怎么做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～问了白问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别问啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多符合夏奈的个性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得就是在说梦话罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去倒垃圾  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间你要打扫好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？哪里变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话变多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？我主动搭话的时候她总是无视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋她以前不喜欢跟别人有过多接触呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真你也变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完全是个伪娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夏奈非要我穿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加遗传爸爸的服务精神使然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天要去千秋家写作业  羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈有没有叫阿珍一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你也要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…今天我也可以一起去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  吉野  内田也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎么欺负他也不会觉得有趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？阿真…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到千秋的同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以堂堂正正的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再受夏奈你的摆布了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从妈妈那遗传的男子气概是绝不允许那种行为的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没同意啊  这可是我家！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然刚到没多久  你还是赶紧滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你有异议！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈让我把这个给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:10:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是阿珍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是朝气十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我也不明白是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号舰严重受损  我军阵形已经崩溃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  出动新型机  无论如何要守住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Class Copper已做好离舰准备  舰桥请指示！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  夏奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的变装完美吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  我问这身变装完美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  还算是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被千秋揭穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田知道我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吉野呢  难不成已经被她发现了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:11:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你慌个什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意被揭穿的话就别干了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样好像是我逼着你穿女装似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你是自由的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有可以自由翱翔宇宙的翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然搞不懂你在说什么…总之没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍你是中学生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是小学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿珍要用敬语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是女孩子  却用这个自称啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…是我的风格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿珍流那么多汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为…酷夏的烈日正在折磨着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  现在是冬天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是察觉到了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:09.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍真是文静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为家里教导有方…有方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来吉野对阿珍有兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好  在做作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也加我一个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？内田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和修一去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  坐在我和吉野中间  帮我抵挡她的攻势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才她就两眼发光的盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是人称「坚不可推」的吉野小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已经怀疑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁给的名号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…千秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着啊  不管是不是被看穿了  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不要与她为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你去哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们班留的作业  很可能是明天我们班要留的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在留作业之前做完  这就是我的战斗方针
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且千秋和吉野的中间  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是可以获得两侧支援的绝佳战场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿珍你要那么慌张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是女孩子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…受不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候罢手了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…是夏奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的年糕也会总有一天会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我喜欢吃年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  你不这么打扮恐怕就进不了我家门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑好的凑在一块就是做得快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得因为没有笨蛋在场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都回去的很早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事…要拜托千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想有所改变  像千秋那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌被叫做原味酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不喜欢吃胡萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会错意啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去买东西了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪方面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得爱说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没觉得自己变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我不认为换个外号人就会变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么沮丧  主要还是看自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是修一  也是有优点的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？哪方面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问哪方面嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要说的话…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急啊…你头脑不差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想说笨蛋才有个性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐躺你身边你就无视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一亿日元而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我梦见千秋你吧哩吧哩的吃胡萝卜条了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后好像又吃了什么好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  这里刚好放着我梦见的胡萝卜条呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了你  一边儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  千秋  请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不先吃了这个  也许就吃不到好东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  换洗衣服我放这里了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:17:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是变了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有人说我变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我想就是变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家在一起会不知不觉受到影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡就来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是说对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你对不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃螃蟹啊  要把这壳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  要把壳这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…看错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是胡萝卜条  其实是螃蟹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹就是要安安静静的吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说怎么了…奶油花居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油花？又是预知梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你根本没做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做是做了  可我忘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在等人吐槽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什么都没看见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管吗？真不管吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道能忍到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们偷偷摸摸的说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上…好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业带来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:19:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到作业…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…现在在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,～再来一碗～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把领带系紧了  保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇～春香为我做了便当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么打我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要抢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂啊  你不是为了让春香吃才每天做便当的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一次都没送出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃春香的便当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想让春香吃你做的便当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水前辈  今天的社团活动…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希！作为参考我问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是吃的那方还是被吃的那方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…应该是吃的那方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  不要因为想脱身就乱说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为他太恶心…呃  太有魄力才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你真是丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂  你本该是个做任何事都拼尽全力的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在的你却迷失了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想一想  你渴望的到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底渴望什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  我到底应该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把领带系好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你  便当都一塌糊涂了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么赔我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才踢了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢了又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…这就是答案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是踢还是打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃还是被吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是二选一的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我两边都要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我是保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一塌糊涂  也照吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:21:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有认为喝醋就会让身体变软的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼骨沾到醋确实会变软
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人骨和鱼骨可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醋会在人体内分解成炭酸和水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.47,0:23:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是趁早放弃这念头去做柔体运动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:45.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第10碗  「舍华求实的年纪」
